Package: binomial
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Quantifying Success in Fixed Random Trial
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lucy Brooke
Maintainer: Lucy Brooke <lucybrooke@berkeley.edu>
Description: Functions to compute and visualize binomial distributions for 
    given trials and probabilities; functions to calculate related 
    summary values (mean, variance, mode, skewness, kurtosis); function to 
    create object of class "binvar"
